### MCP Server - Health
GET {{MCP_BASE_URL}}/health

### List MCP Tools
GET {{MCP_BASE_URL}}/mcp/v1/tools

### Create a sample job (adjust body as needed)
POST {{MCP_BASE_URL}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toolId": "example-tool",
  "input": { "sequence": "MKT..." },
  "metadata": { "note": "sample job from REST Client" }
}

### Get jobs
GET {{MCP_BASE_URL}}/api/jobs

### Get a specific job (replace :id)
GET {{MCP_BASE_URL}}/api/jobs/:id
